z\u0142owski (volleyball)|Micha\u0142 Koz\u0142owski]]||align=right|{{Birth date and age|1985|2|16}}||setter\n|-\n|  ||align=left|  ||align=right|{{Birth date and age|1900|1|1}}||\n|-\n|  ||align=left|  ||align=right|{{Birth date and age|1900|1|1}}||\n|-\n|  ||align=left|  ||align=right|{{Birth date and age|1900|1|1}}||\n|-\n|  ||align=left|  ||align=right|{{Birth date and age|1900|1|1}}||\n|-\n|  ||align=left|  ||align=right|{{Birth date and age|1900|1|1}}||\n|-\n|  ||align=left|  ||align=right|{{Birth date and age|1900|1|1}}||\n|-\n|  ||align=left|  ||align=right|{{Birth date and age|1900|1|1}}||\n|-\n|  ||align=left|  ||align=right|{{Birth date and age|1900|1|1}}||\n|-\n|  ||align=left|  ||align=right|{{Birth date and age|1900|1|1}}||\n|-\n|}\n\n==Notable players==\n{|\n|- style=\"vertical-align: top;\"\n|\n* '''2018\u20132019''' {{flagicon|POL}} [[Bartosz Kurek]]\n* '''2017\u2013present''' {{flagicon|POL}} [[Andrzej Wrona]]\n* '''2017\u2013present''' {{flagicon|POL}} [[Damian Wojtaszek]]\n* '''2017\u2013present''' {{flagicon|POL}} [[Bartosz Kwolek]]\n* '''2017\u2013present''' {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Antoine Brizard]]\n* '''2019\u2013present''' {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Kevin Tillie]]\n* '''2019\u2013present''' {{flagicon|POL}} [[Piotr Nowakowski]]\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==See also==\n* [[Volleyball in Poland]]\n* [[Sports in Poland]]\n{{Polish Men's Volleyball League}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Onico Warszawa}}\n[[Category:Polish volleyball clubs]]\n[[Category:Volleyball clubs established in 2017]]\n[[Category:Sport in Warsaw]]\n[[Category:Sport in Masovian Voivodeship]]\n[[Category:2017 establishments in Poland]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox volleyball club\n| clubname    = VERVA Warszawa<br> ORLEN Paliwa \n| short name  = \n| nickname    = \n| image       = VervaWarszawaLogo.jpg\n| fullname    = VERVA Warszawa ORLEN Paliwa\n| founded     = 1954\n| dissolved   = \n| ground      = [[Torwar Hall]], [[Warszawa]]\n| capacity    = 5,804\n| chairman    = {{flagicon|POL}} Ber